   Studentjobs.gov
   http://www.studentjobs.gov/
   Your one stop to find special opportunities for students in the Federal
   government. Learn about co-ops, internships, summer jobs, the
   Outstanding Scholars Program, volunteer opportunities, and plenty of
   part-time and full-time jobs.
   Related Topics: Internships  Student job programs  Environment  Health
   care  Education  Poverty  Children
   __________________________________________________________________


