   The Digital Classroom (Nat'l Archives and Records Admin)
   http://www.nara.gov/education/classrm.html
   To encourage teachers of students at all levels to use archival
   documents in the classroom, the Digital Classroom provides materials
   from the National Archives and methods for teaching with primary
   sources.
   Related Topics: Graduate/professional  Education  Executive branch
   Academic resources
