   AmericaReads (US Dept of Education)
   http://www.ed.gov/inits/americareads/coluniv.html
   The America Reads Challenge is a national campaign that challenges
   every American to help all our children learn to read, including
   English Language Learners and students with disabilities. Be a
   volunteer and tutor children in reading!
   Related Topics: Education  Poverty  Children
